_sText:
As the terrorists, you'll have to bomb one of two possible targets on the map. Target A is located on the roof of the big building, B point is located on the CT Spawn area, inside a small room wich contains a gas deposit.
As the counter-strike forces, you'll have to erradicate any possible menace from the nearby installations. Be careful, that could be a nest of campers ;)
Done by Smiker AKA Nishi (SGS & NSN Team).
